data.description: All brick, updated Benson tudor sitting on 0.25 acre lot! Beautiful hardwood floors and arched doorways greet you as you walk through the front door. Beautiful family room has fireplace, crown molding and great natural sunlight. Spacious formal dining room is perfect for large gatherings and open to main living area and additional sitting room at the back of the home. Wall to wall windows in the sitting room make for a perfect place to relax or set up an office. Beautifully updated kitchen has great cabinet space, stainless appliances, quartz counters, ceramic tile and eating area. 2 spacious BR's on the main floor (one w/ walk-in closet) and full bathroom. Private 2nd floor has 2 additional BR's (one w/ walk-in closet) and a 2nd, full bathroom. Newly finished lower level has open living area, wetbar, 3/4 bathroom and great storage. Enjoy the outdoors from the large, flat, fenced backyard or the spacious front porch. New HVAC in 2019, some newer windows and washer and dryer stay.
